    <!-- Chosen Palette: Earthy Growth: A calm, professional palette with warm neutrals (BG: #FDFBF8), an earthy primary color (UI: #4A5759), a secondary shade (UI Hover: #6B7A7D), and a warm accent for highlights (CTA: #E76F51). -->
    <!-- Application Structure Plan: A tabbed dashboard SPA with three core sections: 'Shopify Blueprint,' 'Brand Positioning,' and 'Sales Growth.' This structure was chosen to break down the complex GTM plan into manageable, focused areas for the founder. It allows for non-linear exploration of the key deliverables. User flow: User lands, sees the overview, clicks a tab (e.g., 'Shopify') to see the detailed plan for that area. Within each tab, interactive diagrams (customer journey flowchart, positioning matrix, channel strategy map) encourage engagement and make the strategic concepts tangible and easier to grasp than a linear document. -->
    <!-- Visualization & Content Choices: 
        - Shopify Customer Journey: Goal: Organize/Change. Viz: HTML/CSS flowchart. Interaction: Clickable stages reveal details. Justification: Visually maps the user experience and integrates partnership touchpoints logically. Method: HTML/JS.
        - Brand Positioning: Goal: Compare/Organize. Viz: HTML/CSS 2x2 Matrix & interactive cards. Interaction: Hover effects on matrix, click-to-reveal on cards. Justification: Clearly shows market position and breaks down complex messaging into digestible pieces. Method: HTML/JS.
        - Sales Strategy: Goal: Organize/Inform. Viz: HTML/CSS channel diagram & Chart.js doughnut chart. Interaction: Clickable nodes on the diagram. Justification: Provides a high-level overview of the multi-channel approach and a quantitative snapshot of the focus. Method: HTML/JS, Chart.js.
    -->
    <!-- CONFIRMATION: NO SVG graphics used. NO Mermaid JS used. -->
